---
/**
 * CanopyScene — the home's single hand-drawn image (slice-3.8 · 円花
 * keystone made real · wreath composition).
 *
 * Vision (Rika 2026-07-09, tightened): a singular minimalist sumi-e
 * image — bold ensō stroke as the container, cherry-blossom branches
 * hanging DIRECTLY from the ensō (not from a separate canopy inside),
 * larger blossoms per reference, and a small 円花 hanko seal baked
 * into the composition. Wreath-style asymmetry per fukinsei — the
 * left side of the ensō is "carried" by sakura, the right is bare
 * ink stroke.
 *
 * Layers (kept spare · yugen simplicity):
 *   · Panel-style header (円 · canopy + subtitle) at top
 *   · The ensō (bold minimalist single stroke · unchanged from 3.5/3.7)
 *   · Cherry-blossom wreath — one main branch descending from the ensō
 *     top-left, curving around the left side · larger 5-petal sakura
 *     blossoms clustered in 3 groups along the branch (Isson-hairline
 *     branch, blooms in canonical pastels, ink stamens)
 *   · A smaller counter-branch hanging from the top-right of the ensō
 *     for balance
 *   · 円花 hanko seal at bottom-right (poppy square with white 円花
 *     kanji · maker's mark register)
 *   · Isson magpie (small silhouette perched on the ensō right edge)
 *   · Kernel voice · "held long enough to become"
 *   · Light beam (dashed hairline) falling to a small poppy port —
 *     "the light lands here" seal at the bottom centre
 *
 * Retired in this slice: canopy arches + leaf ovals · paintbrush at
 * ensō start · both embroidery needles · previous 3 hanging sprigs +
 * their cascade buds · light-lands flower bed cloth + silk-moiré +
 * 3 tall-stem flowers.
 *
 * Wabi-sabi principles held: fukinsei · kanso · shizen · yugen · seijaku.
 * One fluid intention.
 */
---
<figure class="scene">
  <svg width="820" height="440" viewBox="0 0 820 440" role="img" aria-labelledby="scene-t" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet">
    <title id="scene-t">A minimalist sumi-e ensō with a cherry-blossom branch hanging from its top-left curving down around the interior, larger 5-petal sakura blossoms clustered along it; a small counter-branch hangs from the top-right for balance; a red 円花 maker's-seal sits at the bottom-right; a small Isson magpie perches on the ensō; a dashed light beam falls to a small poppy seal at the bottom centre marked "the light lands here".</title>

    {/* — Panel-style header (kanji + subtitle) — */}
    <text class="hero-kanji" x="412" y="24" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" letter-spacing="0.5" opacity="0.88">円 · canopy</text>
    <text class="hero-sub" x="412" y="44" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-style="italic" opacity="0.6">the container and the light</text>

    {/* — THE ENSŌ · bold minimalist single-brushstroke circle — */}
    <g class="enso-container" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M 700 92 C 540 68, 300 64, 156 106 C 46 152, 24 268, 90 358 C 178 424, 402 438, 590 414 C 710 394, 782 322, 782 236 C 782 178, 748 122, 712 96"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="2.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55"/>
      <path d="M 700 92 C 540 68, 300 64, 156 106 C 46 152, 24 268, 90 358 C 178 424, 402 438, 590 414 C 710 394, 782 322, 782 236 C 782 178, 748 122, 712 96"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.32"/>
      {/* dry-brush tail at 1 o'clock */}
      <path d="M 712 96 C 720 94, 728 96, 734 100" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.9" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.48"/>
      <path d="M 720 92 C 726 91, 730 91, 734 92" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.4" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.32"/>
      <path d="M 726 88 C 730 87, 733 87, 736 88" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.28" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.22"/>
    </g>

    {/* — 円花 WREATH · MAIN LEFT BRANCH — hangs from the ensō top-left,
        curves down through the interior toward the bottom-left arc.
        Fukinsei asymmetry: the left side is "carried" by sakura;
        the right side of the ensō stays bare ink. */}
    <g class="wreath-main" aria-hidden="true">
      {/* main sumi-e branch · thicker calligraphic ink · tapering as it descends */}
      <path d="M 148 108 C 156 148, 168 190, 186 226 C 208 268, 236 296, 268 314"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="2.2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.78"/>
      {/* subtle inner shadow along the branch for sumi-e depth */}
      <path d="M 148 108 C 156 148, 168 190, 186 226 C 208 268, 236 296, 268 314"
        stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.8" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.32"/>
      {/* small side-twig off the branch mid-descent */}
      <path d="M 190 220 C 178 224, 168 232, 160 244"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.68"/>
      {/* second small side-twig lower down */}
      <path d="M 244 302 C 254 306, 264 306, 274 302"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.8" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.62"/>

      {/* — CLUSTER 1 · upper · densest cluster near the branch origin —
          Four larger 5-petal sakura blossoms in 紫 lavender with ink stamens
          and paradox smile in the primary bloom. */}
      {/* primary large blossom · paradox smile hidden inside */}
      <g transform="translate(168 138)">
        <g fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.82">
          <path d="M 0 -8.5 C 3.4 -7.6, 4.5 -2.8, 2.3 -0.8 C 0.7 0.5, -0.7 0.5, -2.3 -0.8 C -4.5 -2.8, -3.4 -7.6, 0 -8.5 Z"/>
          <path d="M 8.1 -2.8 C 9.6 0.5, 7.2 4.6, 3.8 4.1 C 2 3.8, 0.5 2.3, 0.6 0.7 C 2 -1, 5.1 -3.4, 8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
          <path d="M 5 6.7 C 2 8.9, -2 7.2, -2.3 4 C -2.3 2.3, -0.8 0.9, 0.9 1 C 3 2.2, 5.6 4, 5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -5 6.7 C -7.5 4.2, -6.5 -0.6, -3.4 -1 C -1.4 -1, -0.6 0.5, -0.7 2.2 C -1.7 4.3, -3.8 6.5, -5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -8.1 -2.8 C -6.7 -6.2, -2.8 -6.7, -1.4 -4.5 C -0.5 -2.8, -0.7 -0.8, -2.5 0 C -4.8 0.2, -7.5 -1.1, -8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.8" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.94"/>
        <circle cx="0" cy="-1.15" r="0.35" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="0.9" cy="-0.35" r="0.35" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="0.55" cy="0.9" r="0.35" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="-0.55" cy="0.9" r="0.35" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.75"/>
        <circle cx="-0.9" cy="-0.35" r="0.35" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.75"/>
        <path d="M -0.8 1.15 C -0.45 1.55, 0.45 1.55, 0.8 1.15" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.35" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
      </g>
      {/* secondary blossom · upper right */}
      <g transform="translate(190 122) scale(0.75)">
        <g fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.75">
          <path d="M 0 -8.5 C 3.4 -7.6, 4.5 -2.8, 2.3 -0.8 C 0.7 0.5, -0.7 0.5, -2.3 -0.8 C -4.5 -2.8, -3.4 -7.6, 0 -8.5 Z"/>
          <path d="M 8.1 -2.8 C 9.6 0.5, 7.2 4.6, 3.8 4.1 C 2 3.8, 0.5 2.3, 0.6 0.7 C 2 -1, 5.1 -3.4, 8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
          <path d="M 5 6.7 C 2 8.9, -2 7.2, -2.3 4 C -2.3 2.3, -0.8 0.9, 0.9 1 C 3 2.2, 5.6 4, 5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -5 6.7 C -7.5 4.2, -6.5 -0.6, -3.4 -1 C -1.4 -1, -0.6 0.5, -0.7 2.2 C -1.7 4.3, -3.8 6.5, -5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -8.1 -2.8 C -6.7 -6.2, -2.8 -6.7, -1.4 -4.5 C -0.5 -2.8, -0.7 -0.8, -2.5 0 C -4.8 0.2, -7.5 -1.1, -8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.5" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.92"/>
      </g>
      {/* tertiary blossom · overlapping lower-left of primary */}
      <g transform="translate(154 156) scale(0.68)">
        <g fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.72">
          <path d="M 0 -8.5 C 3.4 -7.6, 4.5 -2.8, 2.3 -0.8 C 0.7 0.5, -0.7 0.5, -2.3 -0.8 C -4.5 -2.8, -3.4 -7.6, 0 -8.5 Z"/>
          <path d="M 8.1 -2.8 C 9.6 0.5, 7.2 4.6, 3.8 4.1 C 2 3.8, 0.5 2.3, 0.6 0.7 C 2 -1, 5.1 -3.4, 8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
          <path d="M 5 6.7 C 2 8.9, -2 7.2, -2.3 4 C -2.3 2.3, -0.8 0.9, 0.9 1 C 3 2.2, 5.6 4, 5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -5 6.7 C -7.5 4.2, -6.5 -0.6, -3.4 -1 C -1.4 -1, -0.6 0.5, -0.7 2.2 C -1.7 4.3, -3.8 6.5, -5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -8.1 -2.8 C -6.7 -6.2, -2.8 -6.7, -1.4 -4.5 C -0.5 -2.8, -0.7 -0.8, -2.5 0 C -4.8 0.2, -7.5 -1.1, -8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.4" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.92"/>
      </g>
      {/* small teardrop buds along the branch */}
      <path d="M 178 174 C 179 170, 183 170, 184 174 C 183 178, 179 178, 178 174 Z" fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.75"/>
      <path d="M 200 158 C 201 154, 205 154, 206 158 C 205 162, 201 162, 200 158 Z" fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.7"/>
      <path d="M 148 148 C 149 144, 153 144, 154 148 C 153 152, 149 152, 148 148 Z" fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.68"/>

      {/* — CLUSTER 2 · mid-branch · 珊瑚 coral (poppy family) —
          Three medium blossoms + a couple of buds. Coral fits the poppy
          register + adds warm colour across the wreath. */}
      <g transform="translate(198 226)">
        <g fill="#e46b6b" opacity="0.8">
          <path d="M 0 -7 C 2.8 -6.3, 3.7 -2.3, 1.9 -0.7 C 0.5 0.5, -0.5 0.5, -1.9 -0.7 C -3.7 -2.3, -2.8 -6.3, 0 -7 Z"/>
          <path d="M 6.7 -2.3 C 8 0.5, 6 4.2, 3.1 3.7 C 1.6 3.5, 0.4 2, 0.5 0.6 C 1.6 -0.9, 4.2 -2.8, 6.7 -2.3 Z"/>
          <path d="M 4.2 5.6 C 1.6 7.5, -1.6 6.1, -1.9 3.4 C -1.9 2, -0.7 0.7, 0.7 0.8 C 2.5 1.8, 4.7 3.5, 4.2 5.6 Z"/>
          <path d="M -4.2 5.6 C -6.3 3.5, -5.4 -0.5, -2.8 -0.9 C -1.2 -0.9, -0.5 0.5, -0.6 1.9 C -1.4 3.6, -3.2 5.4, -4.2 5.6 Z"/>
          <path d="M -6.7 -2.3 C -5.6 -5.1, -2.3 -5.6, -1.2 -3.7 C -0.5 -2.3, -0.7 -0.7, -2.1 0 C -4 0.2, -6.3 -0.9, -6.7 -2.3 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.5" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.94"/>
        <circle cx="0" cy="-0.95" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="0.9" cy="-0.3" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="0.55" cy="0.85" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="-0.55" cy="0.85" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="-0.9" cy="-0.3" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <path d="M -0.7 1.15 C -0.4 1.5, 0.4 1.5, 0.7 1.15" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.32" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.55"/>
      </g>
      {/* secondary coral · side-twig tip */}
      <g transform="translate(160 246) scale(0.72)">
        <g fill="#e46b6b" opacity="0.72">
          <path d="M 0 -7 C 2.8 -6.3, 3.7 -2.3, 1.9 -0.7 C 0.5 0.5, -0.5 0.5, -1.9 -0.7 C -3.7 -2.3, -2.8 -6.3, 0 -7 Z"/>
          <path d="M 6.7 -2.3 C 8 0.5, 6 4.2, 3.1 3.7 C 1.6 3.5, 0.4 2, 0.5 0.6 C 1.6 -0.9, 4.2 -2.8, 6.7 -2.3 Z"/>
          <path d="M 4.2 5.6 C 1.6 7.5, -1.6 6.1, -1.9 3.4 C -1.9 2, -0.7 0.7, 0.7 0.8 C 2.5 1.8, 4.7 3.5, 4.2 5.6 Z"/>
          <path d="M -4.2 5.6 C -6.3 3.5, -5.4 -0.5, -2.8 -0.9 C -1.2 -0.9, -0.5 0.5, -0.6 1.9 C -1.4 3.6, -3.2 5.4, -4.2 5.6 Z"/>
          <path d="M -6.7 -2.3 C -5.6 -5.1, -2.3 -5.6, -1.2 -3.7 C -0.5 -2.3, -0.7 -0.7, -2.1 0 C -4 0.2, -6.3 -0.9, -6.7 -2.3 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.3" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.92"/>
      </g>

      {/* — CLUSTER 3 · lower · 金 gold — smaller pair of blossoms + buds
          at the branch tip. Balances the composition downward. */}
      <g transform="translate(272 308) scale(0.85)">
        <g fill="#e8c15a" opacity="0.78">
          <path d="M 0 -6 C 2.4 -5.4, 3.2 -2, 1.6 -0.6 C 0.4 0.4, -0.4 0.4, -1.6 -0.6 C -3.2 -2, -2.4 -5.4, 0 -6 Z"/>
          <path d="M 5.7 -1.9 C 6.9 0.4, 5.1 3.6, 2.7 3.2 C 1.4 3, 0.4 1.8, 0.5 0.5 C 1.4 -0.8, 3.6 -2.4, 5.7 -1.9 Z"/>
          <path d="M 3.5 4.9 C 1.4 6.5, -1.4 5.3, -1.7 2.9 C -1.6 1.7, -0.6 0.6, 0.6 0.7 C 2.1 1.5, 4 3, 3.5 4.9 Z"/>
          <path d="M -3.5 4.9 C -5.3 3, -4.6 -0.4, -2.4 -0.8 C -1 -0.8, -0.4 0.4, -0.5 1.6 C -1.2 3.1, -2.7 4.7, -3.5 4.9 Z"/>
          <path d="M -5.7 -1.9 C -4.8 -4.4, -2 -4.8, -1 -3.2 C -0.4 -2, -0.6 -0.6, -1.8 0 C -3.4 0.2, -5.4 -0.8, -5.7 -1.9 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.3" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.92"/>
        <circle cx="0" cy="-0.8" r="0.26" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="0.75" cy="-0.25" r="0.26" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="0.45" cy="0.7" r="0.26" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="-0.45" cy="0.7" r="0.26" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
        <circle cx="-0.75" cy="-0.25" r="0.26" fill="var(--ink-soft)" opacity="0.72"/>
      </g>
      {/* buds near the tip cluster */}
      <path d="M 262 296 C 263 292, 267 292, 268 296 C 267 300, 263 300, 262 296 Z" fill="#e8c15a" opacity="0.72"/>
      <path d="M 284 316 C 285 312, 289 312, 290 316 C 289 320, 285 320, 284 316 Z" fill="#e8c15a" opacity="0.68"/>
    </g>

    {/* — 円花 WREATH · SMALL RIGHT COUNTER-BRANCH — hangs briefly from
        the ensō top-right, carries a small cluster of blossoms for the
        wabi-sabi asymmetry (not equal to left; just enough to balance). */}
    <g class="wreath-right" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M 720 108 C 714 128, 706 146, 694 162"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.72"/>
      {/* small side-twig */}
      <path d="M 704 148 C 712 152, 720 154, 726 158"
        stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.7" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" opacity="0.6"/>
      {/* small lavender blossom at the tip */}
      <g transform="translate(694 168) scale(0.65)">
        <g fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.75">
          <path d="M 0 -8.5 C 3.4 -7.6, 4.5 -2.8, 2.3 -0.8 C 0.7 0.5, -0.7 0.5, -2.3 -0.8 C -4.5 -2.8, -3.4 -7.6, 0 -8.5 Z"/>
          <path d="M 8.1 -2.8 C 9.6 0.5, 7.2 4.6, 3.8 4.1 C 2 3.8, 0.5 2.3, 0.6 0.7 C 2 -1, 5.1 -3.4, 8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
          <path d="M 5 6.7 C 2 8.9, -2 7.2, -2.3 4 C -2.3 2.3, -0.8 0.9, 0.9 1 C 3 2.2, 5.6 4, 5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -5 6.7 C -7.5 4.2, -6.5 -0.6, -3.4 -1 C -1.4 -1, -0.6 0.5, -0.7 2.2 C -1.7 4.3, -3.8 6.5, -5 6.7 Z"/>
          <path d="M -8.1 -2.8 C -6.7 -6.2, -2.8 -6.7, -1.4 -4.5 C -0.5 -2.8, -0.7 -0.8, -2.5 0 C -4.8 0.2, -7.5 -1.1, -8.1 -2.8 Z"/>
        </g>
        <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="1.4" fill="var(--paper-washi)" opacity="0.92"/>
      </g>
      {/* small bud along the twig */}
      <path d="M 727 158 C 728 154, 732 154, 733 158 C 732 162, 728 162, 727 158 Z" fill="#b899c9" opacity="0.7"/>
    </g>

    {/* — Isson magpie · small silhouette perched on the ensō right edge — */}
    <g class="isson-magpie" transform="translate(776 240)" opacity="0.42" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M -8 0 C -6 -3, -2 -4, 2 -3 C 4 -2, 6 -1, 8 0 C 6 1, 4 1.5, 0 1.5 C -4 1.5, -6 1, -8 0 Z" fill="var(--ink)" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.3"/>
      <circle cx="-5" cy="-1.5" r="0.6" fill="var(--paper-washi)"/>
      <circle cx="-5" cy="-1.5" r="0.3" fill="var(--ink)"/>
      <path d="M 8 0 L 18 1" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.7" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <path d="M -3 1.5 L -3 4" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <path d="M -1 1.5 L -1 4" stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
    </g>

    {/* — Kernel voice · SceneWeaveSeam's shipped register — */}
    <text class="kernel-voice" x="412" y="238" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" opacity="0.6" font-style="italic">held long enough to become</text>

    {/* — Light beam · dashed hairline falling from centre-top through the ensō — */}
    <path class="beam" d="M 412 180 C 420 260, 404 340, 412 386" stroke="var(--ink-soft)" stroke-width="0.7" fill="none" stroke-dasharray="1.5 7" opacity="0.62" />

    {/* — Small poppy port at the base · where the light lands — */}
    <circle class="port-ring" cx="412" cy="392" r="8" />
    <circle class="port-fill" cx="412" cy="392" r="3" />
    <text class="hand-label hand-label--accent" x="418" y="416" font-size="18">the light lands here</text>

    {/* — 円花 HANKO SEAL · maker's mark at bottom-right —
        Small poppy-red rounded square with white 円花 kanji stacked
        vertically. Reads as: the maker's seal · circle-flower · the
        keystone concept made literal. */}
    <g class="enka-seal" transform="translate(722 388)" aria-hidden="true">
      <rect x="0" y="0" width="26" height="30" rx="2.5" fill="var(--poppy)" opacity="0.88"
        stroke="var(--ink)" stroke-width="0.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      <text x="13" y="13.5" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Noto Serif JP', 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif" font-size="10" fill="var(--paper-washi)" font-weight="500">円</text>
      <text x="13" y="26" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Noto Serif JP', 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif" font-size="10" fill="var(--paper-washi)" font-weight="500">花</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
</figure>
<style>
  .scene { margin: 0; }
  .scene svg { width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .beam { opacity: 0.62; }
  /* panel-style header + kernel voice type */
  .hero-kanji { font-family: "Noto Serif JP", var(--display); fill: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .hero-sub { font-family: var(--serif); fill: var(--ink-soft); font-style: italic; }
  .kernel-voice { font-family: var(--hand); fill: var(--ink-soft); }
  /* the hand-label accent — the poppy-red seal register */
  .hand-label--accent { font-family: var(--hand); fill: var(--poppy); }
  /* Slice-3.5 · animations retired for sumi-e discipline — no motion. */
</style>
